Some kind of bogus cloth simulation.


Prerequisites:
   GLFW  installed -> www.glfw.org


Make and Install:
   Get Gamgine   -> https://github.com/dan-t/Gamgine
   Get cabal-dev -> cabal install cabal-dev

   cd clothsim
   cabal-dev add-source <Path-To-Gamgine-Dir>
   cabal-dev install


Usage:
   clothsim


Control:
   Pick the cloth by holding the left mouse button pressed
